cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.MM 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper deals with fashion recommendation systems that involve visual embeddings of garments, which falls under the domain of computer vision. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The proposed approach involves the use of a graph neural network, which is a popular machine learning technique. 
3. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper deals with recommending fashion items to users, which can be seen as an information retrieval task. 
4. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper involves the use of a style classifier, which can be seen as a natural language processing task. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with recommending visually-collocated fashion items, which can be seen as a multimedia task.
